                     <interp inst="t18390408-1265-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="housebreaking"></interp>for feloniously break<lb></lb>ing and entering the dwelling-house of <persName id="t18390408-name-655" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18390408-name-655" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
